{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "jobnow-api-sprint1",
		"name": "JobyNow API - Sprint 1",
		"description": "Collection des endpoints REST API pour JobyNow V2 - Sprint 1\n\nInclut:\n- JNV-2: Inscription entreprise\n- JNV-15: Création offre d'emploi\n- JNV-22: Postuler à une offre\n\nBase URL: {{base_url}}",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Authentication",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "[JNV-2] Register Entreprise",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"// Save token from response",
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.token) {",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"auth_token\", jsonData.data.token);",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"entreprise_id\", jsonData.data.entreprise.id);",
									"        console.log(\"✅ Token saved: \" + jsonData.data.token);",
									"    }",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							},
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"entreprise@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"SecurePass123\",\n    \"password_confirmation\": \"SecurePass123\",\n    \"raison_social\": \"Tech Solutions SARL\",\n    \"adresse\": \"123 Rue de la Paix, 75001 Paris\",\n    \"telephone\": \"0123456789\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register/entreprise",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"auth",
								"register",
								"entreprise"
							]
						},
						"description": "Créer un compte entreprise avec profil complet.\n\n**Réponse attendue:**\n- Code: 201 Created\n- Token Sanctum pour authentification\n- Informations entreprise créée"
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Register Candidat",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"// Save token from response",
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.token) {",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"auth_token\", jsonData.data.token);",
									"        pm.environment.set(\"candidat_id\", jsonData.data.user.id);",
									"        console.log(\"✅ Token saved: \" + jsonData.data.token);",
									"    }",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							},
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"candidat@example.com\",\n    \"password\": \"SecurePass123\",\n    \"password_confirmation\": \"SecurePass123\",\n    \"nom\": \"Dupont\",\n    \"prenom\": \"Jean\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register/candidat",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"auth",
								"register",
								"candidat"
							]
						},
						"description": "Créer un compte candidat.\n\n**Réponse attendue:**\n- Code: 201 Created\n- Token Sanctum pour authentification\n- Informations candidat créé"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			],
			"description": "Endpoints d'authentification et inscription"
		},
		{
			"name": "Job Offers",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "[JNV-15] Create Job Offer",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "bearer",
							"bearer": [
								{
									"key": "token",
									"value": "{{auth_token}}",
									"type": "string"
								}
							]
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							},
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"titre\": \"Développeur Laravel Senior\",\n    \"description\": \"Nous recherchons un développeur Laravel expérimenté pour rejoindre notre équipe dynamique. Vous travaillerez sur des projets innovants en utilisant les dernières technologies.\",\n    \"competences_requises\": [\n        \"PHP 8.2+\",\n        \"Laravel 11\",\n        \"MySQL\",\n        \"Vue.js\",\n        \"Git\",\n        \"REST API\"\n    ],\n    \"localisation\": \"Paris, France (Hybride)\",\n    \"salaire\": \"45k-60k EUR\",\n    \"type_contrat\": \"CDI\",\n    \"date_expiration\": \"2026-06-30\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/offres",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"offres"
							]
						},
						"description": "Créer une nouvelle offre d'emploi (authentification entreprise requise).\n\n**Headers requis:**\n- Authorization: Bearer {token}\n\n**Champs obligatoires:**\n- titre\n- description\n- type_contrat (CDI, CDD, Stage, Freelance)\n\n**Réponse attendue:**\n- Code: 201 Created\n- Détails de l'offre créée"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			],
			"description": "Gestion des offres d'emploi (entreprises)",
			"auth": {
				"type": "bearer",
				"bearer": [
					{
						"key": "token",
						"value": "{{auth_token}}",
						"type": "string"
					}
				]
			}
		},
		{
			"name": "Job Applications",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "[JNV-22] Apply for Job",
					"request": {
						"auth": {
							"type": "bearer",
							"bearer": [
								{
									"key": "token",
									"value": "{{auth_token}}",
									"type": "string"
								}
							]
						},
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json",
								"type": "text"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "formdata",
							"formdata": [
								{
									"key": "offre_id",
									"value": "1",
									"description": "ID de l'offre d'emploi",
									"type": "text"
								},
								{
									"key": "cv",
									"description": "Fichier CV (PDF, DOC, DOCX max 5MB)",
									"type": "file",
									"src": []
								},
								{
									"key": "lettre_motivation",
									"value": "Je suis très intéressé par ce poste car il correspond parfaitement à mon profil et à mes aspirations professionnelles. Fort de 5 ans d'expérience en développement Laravel, je maîtrise l'ensemble des technologies mentionnées dans l'offre.",
									"description": "Lettre de motivation (optionnel)",
									"type": "text"
								}
							]
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/candidatures",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"candidatures"
							]
						},
						"description": "Postuler à une offre d'emploi avec CV (authentification candidat requise).\n\n**Headers requis:**\n- Authorization: Bearer {token}\n\n**Champs obligatoires:**\n- offre_id (integer)\n- cv (file: PDF, DOC, DOCX max 5MB)\n\n**Champs optionnels:**\n- lettre_motivation (text)\n\n**Réponse attendue:**\n- Code: 201 Created\n- ID de la candidature\n- Statut: en_attente\n\n**Note:** Utiliser form-data pour l'upload de fichier"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			],
			"description": "Gestion des candidatures (candidats)",
			"auth": {
				"type": "bearer",
				"bearer": [
					{
						"key": "token",
						"value": "{{auth_token}}",
						"type": "string"
					}
				]
			}
		},
		{
			"name": "User Info",
